Subject: IUGU - DPI not being enabled through groups
Description:
Hello Team,

As the title says, DPI is enabled in any case. In globals, computer or even in user, but cannot be enabled in groups. Let me know if you have anything to test or availability for tuesday or wednesday after 10h BRT.

Best regards,
What_We_Know__c: DPI can be enabled in Device Control -> Global, computer or even in user, but cannot be enabled in groups.
Solution_Comment__c: the test computer had custom settings, after restoring global settings, group settings were successfuly applied
